<chapter id="intro">
  &intro_common;

  <section>
    <title>About this document</title>
    <para>
      This manual discusses the user utilities of &ps;. These include an
      adapted development framework for MPI applications based on <ulink
	url="www.unix.mcs.anl.gov/mpi/mpich/">MPIch</ulink>. Furthermore &ps;'s
      process spawning mechanism is described and the potential ways to steer
      it are presented.
    </para>
    <para>
      For a detailed discussion of the installation and configuration of &ps;
      and the administrators utilities in the standard distribution take a look
      at the <ulink url="../adminguide/index.html" type="dontshow">ParaStation
	Administrators Guide</ulink>. The &ps; programming interfaces
      documentation can be found in the <ulink url="../api/index.html"
	type="dontshow">API reference</ulink>..
    </para>

    <para>
      This document describes version 3.2 of the &ps; software for Myrinet and
      version 1.0 of ParaStation FE.
    </para>
  </section>
</chapter>

